Hemlock was originally written at Carnegie Mellon University as part of the
CMU Common Lisp project and placed in the public domain.

Original CMU authors include: Bill Chiles, Rob MacLachlan, Skef Wholey,
William Lott, Ivan Vazquez, Bill Maddox, Jamie W. Zawinski, Christopher Hoover,
Blaine Burks, and others.

Additional contributors: Gilbert Baumann, Luke Gorrie, Brian Downing,
Taylor Campbell, Edi Weitz, Matthias Koeppe, Tobias C. Rittweiler,
Nikodemus Siivola, Julian Squires, David Lichteblau, Paul Foley.

Ported and maintained by bfh (2024-present).
